output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: No visible CMF number, but this doesn't automatically disqualify it as propaganda.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions "George Simion" as a presidential candidate, stating "îl voi vota pe George Simion - preşedinte"
3. Addresses wide population: Yes - It's a paid advertisement on Facebook/Instagram - Targets a large audience (100,001-500,000 people) - Has received significant impressions (25,000-29,999)
4. Electoral objective: Yes - Explicitly promotes voting for George Simion - Uses persuasive language to convince others to vote for him - Presents a clear electoral message with "la aceste alegeri, îl voi vota pe George Simion - preşedinte"
5. Journalism: No - This is clearly an opinion piece with a direct call to action - Doesn't maintain journalistic neutrality - Doesn't provide balanced information
6. Personal opinion: While presented as a personal opinion, it's a paid advertisement meant to influence others, making it propaganda rather than mere personal expression.

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It explicitly promotes a presidential candidate - It's a paid advertisement reaching a large audience - Has a clear electoral objective to influence voting behavior - Uses persuasive messaging to promote a specific candidate - Is not journalistic content but rather campaign material
conclusion.message-for-police: AUR - Sălașu de Sus, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin promovarea unui mesaj de propaganda electorala pentru candidatul George Simion la functia de presedinte, dupa incheierea perioadei de campanie electorala. Postarea cu ID-ul 1089703459529652 contine un indemn explicit de vot ("îl voi vota pe George Simion - preşedinte"), fiind promovata ca reclama platita pe Facebook si Instagram, cu un buget intre 100-199 RON si un impact estimat intre 25.000-29.999 de afisari, dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Mesajul are un evident caracter de propaganda electorala, utilizand argumente persuasive pentru a influenta decizia de vot a alegatorilor in favoarea candidatului AUR la presedintie.
